for purchasable SKUs; quote-first products keep their Cotizar CTA. Move the
cart button into the main nav action row so it's visible on desktop AND mobile
(was hidden in the desktop-only top bar), add it to the mobile menu, and
neutralize its color so it reads correctly on the white navbar.
